This sets up the necessary globals and types. Next, we'll add the policies to the BlogPost type.

```sdl
-- Add policies to the BlogPost type
type BlogPost {
  required title -> str;
  -- Other fields and links

  -- Define a policy named 'view_policy'
  policy view_policy on select using (
    exists(
      -- Assuming BlogPost has a link to Country
      -- This condition checks if the BlogPost's country is the current user's country
      .country = global current_country
    )
  );
};
```
This `view_policy` allows the selection of BlogPost entries only if the country associated with the blog post matches the `current_country` global variable.

